Captioned by
Media Access Group at WGBH

46:39.364 --> 46:42.433
Keep practicing.
Could be faster.

46:42.467 --> 46:45.136
ANNOUNCER: Feud: Bette and Joan.
All-new Sunday at 10:00 on FX.

46:46.972 --> 46:49.841
-HENRY: I'm hungry.
-You're always hungry.
We just ate.

46:51.242 --> 46:53.178
PHILIP:
He has hollow legs.

46:53.211 --> 46:56.814
(laughing)
And a very empty head.

46:56.848 --> 46:58.349
ANNOUNCER: The Americans.

46:58.383 --> 47:01.019
All new Tuesdays at 10:00.
On FX.

47:03.554 --> 47:06.324
MAN: Dateline,
Los Angeles, California, 1947.

47:06.357 --> 47:10.061
FXX, now home
to quasi-incestuous home lives.

47:10.095 --> 47:11.863
I have to get away
from my family.

47:11.897 --> 47:14.032
They're quasi-incestuous
megalomaniacs!

47:14.065 --> 47:16.001
How quasi?

47:16.034 --> 47:18.169
(sighs)
I don't know. A four?

47:18.203 --> 47:20.838
Archer: Dreamland.
All new Wednesdays at 10:00.

47:20.872 --> 47:22.073
On FXX.

47:23.909 --> 47:26.244
(electronic game sounds)

47:26.277 --> 47:27.778
(radio squawks)

47:30.215 --> 47:32.350
WOMAN:
Don't forget your pies.

47:32.383 --> 47:34.886
(sniffles, clears throat)
(clears throat)

47:41.626 --> 47:43.728
(door bell jingling)

47:43.761 --> 47:45.964
(electricity crackling)

47:50.035 --> 47:52.537
Fargo. All-new
Wednesdays at 10:00.

47:52.570 --> 47:53.638
On FX.

48:01.479 --> 48:04.515
MAN: I'm getting paid to learn
how to run a business,

48:04.549 --> 48:07.218
do things when I want
and how I want,

48:07.252 --> 48:10.388
get paid more
than some office job.

48:10.421 --> 48:12.023
I got freedom.

48:12.057 --> 48:14.125
(siren wailing)

48:14.159 --> 48:15.927
Freedom from all of it.

48:19.430 --> 48:21.266
(dog barking)

48:21.299 --> 48:22.633
(siren wailing continues)

48:22.667 --> 48:24.435
(man exhales)
